availableCriteria: Pokemon must be in point value columns (cols 9, 12, 15, etc.)
Pokemon must NOT be in Banned column (col 3)
Pokemon must NOT be marked as Drafted (col 70 = "X")
Pokemon can be Tera Banned (col 6) but still draftable (just can't be Tera Captain)
generationRules.pointValueAssignment: Point value determined by column position (+1 from header column)

statusDetermination.banned: Col 2 = "X" OR Pokemon name in col 3
statusDetermination.teraBanned: Col 5 = "X" OR Pokemon name in col 6
